---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Ara què? - Guia Emocional">
  <main class="pt-32 pb-20 overflow-x-hidden bg-white">
    <section
      class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center"
    >
      <div class="space-y-10 text-center lg:text-left relative">
        <div
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-[#F9C18A]/10 border border-[#F9C18A]/30 rounded-full"
        >
          <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
            <span
              class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-[#F9C18A] opacity-75"
            ></span>
            <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-[#F9C18A]"
            ></span>
          </span>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-[#e69b55] tracking-wide uppercase"
            >Projecte Educatiu 2026</span
          >
        </div>

        <h1
          class="text-7xl md:text-[85px] font-black text-slate-900 leading-[0.85] tracking-tighter"
        >
          Ara Què<span class="text-[#A7D6E9]">?</span><br />
          <span
            class="text-[#F9C18A] font-medium text-4xl md:text-5xl block mt-4 tracking-tight"
          >
            Construint el camí cap a la teva autonomia.
          </span>
        </h1>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center lg:justify-start">
          <a
            href="/landing-page/projecte"
            class="bg-[#A7D6E9] text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-2xl font-bold shadow-xl shadow-sky-100 hover:bg-[#92c5db] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all"
          >
            Descobreix el projecte
          </a>
          <a
            href="/landing-page/com-funciona"
            class="bg-white text-slate-500 border border-slate-200 px-10 py-4 rounded-2xl font-bold hover:bg-slate-50 transition-all"
          >
            Com funciona?
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative flex justify-center lg:justify-end group">
        <div
          class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-full h-full bg-sky-100/50 blur-[120px] rounded-full"
        >
        </div>

        <div
          class="relative w-[290px] h-[620px] bg-slate-950 rounded-[3.5rem] border-[10px] border-slate-950 shadow-2xl overflow-hidden ring-1 ring-white/10"
        >
          <div class="absolute inset-0 z-10">
            <img
              src="/landing-page/images/mockup-app.png"
              alt="App Ara Què"
              class="w-full h-full object-contain bg-[#fdfaf3]"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section
      class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-32 mt-20 border-t border-slate-100"
    >
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-16">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <h3
            class="text-xl font-black text-[#A7D6E9] uppercase tracking-[0.2em]"
          >
            La Solució
          </h3>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
            <strong class="text-slate-900">Ara què?</strong> és una solució tecnològica
            inclusiva dissenyada per millorar l'autonomia de persones amb TEA mitjançant
            rutines visuals.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <h3
            class="text-xl font-black text-[#F9C18A] uppercase tracking-[0.2em]"
          >
            Motivació
          </h3>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
            Integra la <strong class="text-slate-900">gamificació</strong>:
            recompenses digitals que fomenten la independència i el seguiment
            del progrés.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <h3
            class="text-xl font-black text-[#A7D6E9] uppercase tracking-[0.2em]"
          >
            Impacte Social
          </h3>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
            Reduïm l'ansietat davant la incertesa quotidiana, facilitant una
            <strong class="text-slate-900">inclusió social</strong> real i efectiva.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
